題嘅來源</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">跟住Tvb就將呢個中共世界觀套用落美國政府(財政部)度 所以「美國財政部就香港問題...」根本解唔通</span><br />\n<br />\n【詳細分析】<br />\n「問題」係中共語境係有懸疑未決，加上用「問題」frame就可以含糊事件本質，撈埋「有人搞事」等等嘅負面意思。例如「香港問題」，本身香港人唔會覺得中港關係現況有咩大反感，但就係中共淆底，自己frame個香港問題出來搞全面管治乜乜柒柒。「台灣問題」一樣係咁，你問台灣人長期朝野共識係維持現狀，所以對台灣人而言無所謂嘅「台灣問題」，只係中共覺得未攻佔台灣先frame個台灣問題搞乜春野兩岸和平統一。<br />\n<br />\n英文語境絕少會用 Problem/Issue of XXXX去形容國際關係嘅事。據牛津字典，<br />\n//<strong>Problem</strong> <em>(n.)</em> A matter or situation regarded as unwelcome or harmful and needing to be dealt with and overcome.//<br />\n文明世界嘅國際關係沒對與錯得觀點與角度，用Problem去形容具主觀對錯意識。相反Dispute/Crisis/Uprising/Crackdown指涉嘅事件同性質清晰。亦可以直接講晒全件事或唔好加埋啲多餘嘅字。例子有以下英語媒體Heading<br />\n<br />\n<strong>SCMP</strong><br />\nUS sanctions Chinese legislators for national security law on Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<strong>The NY Times</strong><br />\nU.S. Imposes Sanction on Chinese Officials Over Hong Kong Crackdown<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Bloomberg</strong><br />\nU.S. Sanctions New Group of Chinese Officials Over Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Financial Times</strong><br />\nUS puts sanctions on 14 Chinese officials over Hong Kong Crackdown<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Wall Street Journal</strong><br />\nU.S. Adds Senior Chinese Lawmakers to Hong Kong Sanctions Blacklist<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Reuters</strong><br />\nU.S. sanctions 14 Chinese officials over Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">美國(英語世界)並無所謂「香港問題」。財政部亦唔覺得香港有咩要解決。跟聯合聲明玩就有獨立關稅區；破壞香港自治咁就會制裁中共/港共嘅Collaborators去阻嚇。只有美國對港/中政策，冇香港/中國問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">大家要小心中共語言入侵，多啲睇外語媒體唔好比華文傳媒洗腦。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cbe4e6818b5c4299ae2ce611df7b7448047556","tid":2317485,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f59cccd8358445e17797cf987ec3a108911b7b74","tid":2317485,"uid":134323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":